Package: bdl
Type: Package
Date: 2019-08-05
Title: Interface and Tools for 'BDL' API
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Krzysztof", "Kania", email = "K.Kania@stat.gov.pl",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The 'bdl' package is an interface to Local Data Bank('Bank Danych Lokalnych' - 'bdl') API 
    with set of useful tools like quick plotting and map generating using data from data bank. 
